description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has become available with The Patient Engagement team who are looking for an apprentice to support their activities alongside the wider Quality team. The qualification will be a level 3 Business admin course, that can be undertaken at Exeter College or via an external provider.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The suitable applicant will have to demonstrate their ability to be organised, enthusiastic and willing to learn. The Quality team is a busy directorate and looks at many aspects of supporting our patients including engagement, complaints, safety, risk and compliance. You will have the opportunity to support the wider team with a focus on plaudits and patient feedback.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We believe in having a diverse and inclusive workforce which represents the community we serve. We would like to encourage applicants from individuals who identify as being black or from an ethnic minority, LGBTQ+ or disabled.&lt;/p&gt;
